summary:
The Outskirts of Riverwood is currently a very small settlement to the south east of Riverwood. Currently it is only a tent with a bed roll, a small alchemy garden, and an apothecary shop. I will be maintaining this expansion and adding on to it as new ideas come to me.
<br />
<br />Installation: Extract into your Data direc
